OF THE UK 996 W OF SOLE 996 NW ROCKALL AND 996 FAROES WHILST A RIDGE OF
HIGH PRESSURE LIES ACROSS THE UK. THROUGH SATURDAY THESE LOW CENTRES SIMPLIFY
